'''Imerominia''' is a staff member at the [[Library Historical Archive]] in the [[Arceuus]]. She is a horologist who can tell the player more about the [[Twill accord|Royal Accord of Twill]], and the date convention [[Great Kourend]] uses.

She is also spoken to during [[Dragon Slayer II]], where players ask her for information about [[Camorra]].

